        <a class="anchor" id="long-context-eval"></a>
        <h2 class="title is-3">Long-Context Reasoning Evaluation</h2>

        <div class="content has-text-justified">
          <p>
            <span class="dmethod">PERK</span> demonstrates strong performance on long-context
            reasoning tasks, significantly outperforming standard supervised finetuned
            models with in-context reasoning (FT-ICR). We evaluate <span
              class="dmethod">PERK</span
            > in three challenging scenarios: (1) Needles-in-a-Haystack — Reasoning
            with <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2406.10149" target="_blank"
              >BabiLong</a
            >, (2) Drops-in-an-Ocean (DIO), a novel evaluation setting we
            propose, and (3) Multi-Doc QA with <a
              href="https://hotpotqa.github.io/"
              target="_blank">HotpotQA</a
            > and <a
              href="https://nlp.cs.washington.edu/triviaqa/"
              target="_blank">TriviaQA</a
            > for real-world long-context reasoning.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="figure-container">
          <figure class="image tok-figure">
            <img
